IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Curtis Anthony MABBITT and Kristina Marie Mabbitt Upon the Petition of Curtis Anthony Mabbitt, Petitioner-Appellant/Cross-Appellee, And Concerning Kristina Marie Mabbitt n/k/a Kristina Marie Hickcox, Respondent-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 18-0817 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The appellant appeals and the appellee cross-appeals from the order modifying the decree of dissolution of their marriage. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
